scenes.description: A slideshow of fan-submitted message boards featuring artwork and messages of support for various Hololive English members, including Gawr Gura, Mori Calliope, Takanashi Kiara, Ninomae Ina'nis, Watson Amelia, IRyS, Ceres Fauna, Ouro Kronii, Nanashi Mumei, and Hakos Baelz.
A series of official merchandise advertisements for the 'Connect the World' concert, featuring computer hardware, apparel, and collectible figures.
The main visual for the concert is displayed with a notice stating that the performance will be starting soon.
Continuation of the merchandise showcase, featuring concert apparel, light sticks, and accessory sets.
The slideshow returns to displaying fan message boards.
